The '''Triumvirate''' was the name used by [[Spacer/Legends|spacers]] for the three major [[Tunroth]] [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworlds]]: [[Jiroch-Reslia]], [[Jiroch-Saloch]] and [[Jiroch-Kalok]]. The Tunroth of Jiroch-Reslia settled the other two planets when they joined the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] around [[9000 BBY]].

The name was a dedication to the [[Assemblage of Three]] who promoted their colonization.

